Peru is an application for the ATmega328P microcontroller.

Peru manages a Velleman VMA437 OLED display connected via SPI.
Peru is connected to other mpus via the TWI. There is no HC-05.

To build and install the application :-

  $ make
  $ cd ../bali
  $ avril peru

To build and install the application and bootloader :-

  connect the ICSP cable between bali and peru

  $ make image
  $ cd ../bali
  $ (. ./defs.sh && cd ../peru && make avp)

